Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.10,0:01:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,CHECKMATE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,King... Gaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so weakened\Nthat a single hit will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You've taken so much damage that\NHeal Type spells are no longer effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a nudge from a pawn and it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I should warn you that no bluff\Nwill work against my brain and eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This brain contains all the battle data
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that the Heyedras\Nhave gathered on you lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest you stop resisting\Nand die with one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it?\NI won't accept any pleading for your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You called yourself "Ban Palace's\Ngreatest and most powerful guardian."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So why aren't you guarding Ban?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A simple warrior like you\Nwho only sees the battle in front of them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,would never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to educate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The word "defeat"\Ndoesn't exist in my lexicon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Weeding out the weak and wounded
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.33,0:03:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to decrease an enemy's numbers\Nis a rule of combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To enter battle means\Nvictory must be assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My army, once deployed,\Nhas never failed to wipe out an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To fight means to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That is how my army works!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.39,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mystban should be holding off\Nthe Hero and his friends at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll dispose of you weaklings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,then I wipe out the Hero and his friends\Nkeeping Mystban busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I do that, I'll get credit\Nfor wiping out all the intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a lowlife!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's time for you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, perhaps I should let\NMystban struggle a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He always looks down on me\Nand calls me the "Cleaner."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He should learn to be grateful to have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the Cleaner of Ban Palace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A metallic lifeform born\Nfrom an Orichalcum chess piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! The Hadorra Royal Guard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already defeated all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more chess pieces\Nthan the ones you've beaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you fought the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't Hadorra the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra isn't a chess piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.84,0:05:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes sense that\Nthe real king is still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, there are pieces come in pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are other Orichalcum warriors\Nbesides the Hadorra Royal Guard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not ones with their own wills like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the king was born with its own will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.57,0:05:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And it appears the king\Nhas finally decided to make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.79,0:05:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're utter filth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not worth leaving alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is why I love\Nfinishing off the dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can end your lives with just a snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.69,0:06:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forth, my pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that! A bum rush\Nby my pawns and he's finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Return!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? I said to return!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He shattered Orichalcum with his fist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That bastard! He did it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're different from Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you babbling about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And you aren't Sigma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In the Hadorra Royal Guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym and Sigma and Albinass...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They were all great warriors\Nwith their own wills!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They were powerful and loyal\Nand willing to die for their master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But your servants are simply pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They're mindless puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You arrogant little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,King Gaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,S-See?! You're barely alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll only take a scratch\Nto take you down! You just got lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him, Bishop! In one sure strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The flame of my life may dwindle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but it can't be extinguished\Nby mere puppets!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Go forth, rook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.83,0:09:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pawns!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, take him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.20,0:09:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not dropping!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That last single point of damage!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-All it should take is\None scratch to deplete it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?! Why doesn't he die\Nfrom all those attacks?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-According to my databank,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:10:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Dark Swordsman Hyunckel's\Nimmortality is nothing but a label!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He should be a mere human!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-In that case...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Super Gaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}L-Look at that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way anyone can safely\Nshatter Orichalcum bare-handed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's... He's beyond all healing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-So how...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can he still move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amazing! The power driving Hyunckel\Nis greater than life itself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's... That's Fortitude!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.23,0:10:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I have are five pawns left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way they can't\Ncause a single point of damage...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I have to admit that he possesses\Nsome kind of supernatural power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My next... My next order is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All return! Return and guard me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... He's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.26,0:11:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just puppets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't help you\Nunless you order them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are like\Nthe king on a chess board.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All you can do\Nis order other pieces around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You use your troops to surround\Nand corner your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your tactical mind\Nis your only real strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really had any power at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't have summoned\Nyour troops back to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Checkmate, Maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's won!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:37.46,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4}GRAND CROSS{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:42.47,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4}AURA KNUCKLE{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,King Access!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can control my pawns with just a finger,\Nbut it's not enough to defeat him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I need to find a definite weakness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, finish them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hym!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! You should just\Nforget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damaged as you are,\Nfalling from here would kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.33,0:13:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough! Just let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,His past data proves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.13,0:14:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,this man can't sacrifice\Nhis friends to save himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means death for you two,\Nhe can't choose his own survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just that kind of fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? He considers me a friend?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that's a mortal weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be a heartless warrior,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but all that compassion and love\Nfrom your friends has made you soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the one weakness\Nof the immortal warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Love?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I discovered that\Nproves how great my mind is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.09,0:14:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's super, super great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I did what Maam did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To think... I could do that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping to at least save you,\Nbut I wasn't strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I'm going to lose\Nfor my compassion or love...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a loss I proudly accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I share that opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's indeed quite the idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I shall take\Nthat last point of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My fist is far greater than any pawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now splatter into pulp, you weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Thud?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Who dares?!\NWh-Who would display such insolence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Such insolence"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what I always do...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.64,0:16:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to scum who fight dishonorably.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I make it a point to impale them\Nwith my Dark Spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Identify yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Land Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Larhart has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Land Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.04,0:16:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Larhart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that miracles\Ncome in twos and threes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Aban, another amazing individual\Nhas returned from the afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My greatest rival,\Nand the friend whose will I carry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Land Rider Larhart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Access!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Larhart. Former Dragon Legion follower\Nand one of the Dragon Masters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master of the spear and original owner\Nof the Dark Armour Spear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}According to my records,\Nhe died in the fight with the Heroes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you lose your way,\Nyou lost soul?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But my magnificent brain\Nobviously contains data on you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already accessed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know all of your attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What sort of data?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly you possess great speed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your greatest attack\Nis your Hakendisutoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.70,0:18:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But, empty-handed,\Nyou have no choice but to evade me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To counter that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That movement...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a good look, Hym.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty fast,\Nbut there's always someone faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Could you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My supposed "great speed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If simply knowing I'm fast was\Nenough to win, things would be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, your other data\Nis probably useless in actual battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.92,0:18:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him, my pawns!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,let me show you for posterity's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the real...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hakendisutoru!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:20:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well! I'll let you\Nhave the victory for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But my army cannot lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I swear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.33,0:20:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take one step\Nfrom that position you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hollow threats don't scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you didn't even notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He already shredded your whole body\Nat an incredible speed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.77,0:20:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.56,0:20:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all trying\Nto trick me, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,King Access!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! This is a psychological trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't trick me\Nwith such uncertain information!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.38,0:21:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You reap what you sow. A fitting end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That king really was a true idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I could have been\None of those pawns!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness I was born\Nas Lord Hadorra's servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.66,0:21:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one in eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this Larhart guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened between him and Hyunckel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.08,0:22:17.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:28.26,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.26,0:22:36.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:45.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.70,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:56.00,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.16,0:23:02.38,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.22,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.38,0:23:15.01,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.18,0:23:20.81,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:26.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one who saved Hyunckel and Hym{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was the Dragon Master, Land Rider Larhart,\Nwho was thought to have died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Larhart dons the Dark Armour Spear\Nand heads off to Dai and the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Meanwhile, in the White Garden,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the stage is set\Nfor the battle against Mystban,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the greatest enemy in the Dark Army.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.35,0:23:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Battle in the White Garden"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
